  Pak Bi2-chiu u7 chit8 tiau5 toa7 ho5, kio3-choe3 Ni-a-ka-la, chit tiau5 tui3 I2-li7-ou5 thau3 kau3 An-tat8-lou7-ou5, chha-put-to 115 li2 poaN3. Tiong-kan u7 chit8 e5 chhut-mia5 e5 phak8-pou3, koaiN5 160 chhioh, ho5-bin7 put-chi2 oeh8, ho5-toe2 e5 chhia5-bin7 sng3 iau2 toa7, tui3 teng2-bin7 kau3 e7-bin7 iok-liok8 25 li2. Ho5 e5 siang-peng5 koaiN5 soaN kia7-kia7, sou2-i2 chui2 teh lau5 put-chi2 kin2, sou2 khi2 e5 eng2 chhin-chhiuN7 hai2--nih-e5 chit8-iuN7. U7 si5 lau5-chui2 saN chhiong, oe7 phun3 kau3 kui2-na7 chhioh koaiN5. Lang5 khia7 ti7 hoaN7-teng2, khoaN3-liau2 kau3 beh gong7--khi3. Ui2-poe3 oa2-kho3 i gau5 siu5, siuN7 beh sun7 lau5 siu5--loh8-khi3, lai5 tit-tioh8 toa7 mia5-siaN. u7 peng5-iu2 khng3 i kong2, ¡§Chui2 lau5 hiah kiong5, lang5 e5 lat8 tong3 i boe7-tiau5, chhiat-chhiat m7-thang loh8-khi3 siu5.¡¨ Ui2-poe3 kong2, ¡§Chhi3-khoaN3, kap i piaN3 chit8 e5 ji7-un7--leh.¡¨ Tui3 an2-ni chit siau-sit thoan5-po3 si3-hng. Kau3 si5, u7 kui2-na7 ban7 lang5, lai5 tiam3 ho5 e5 siang peng5 hoaN7, beh khoaN3 Ui2-poe3 tian2 pun2-su7. Ui2-poe3 tng cheng3-lang5 e5 bin7-cheng5 thng3 saN, thiau3-loh8 chui2, khoaN3-kiN3 i thau5-khak phu5-chhut chui2-bin7 chit8 pai2, tu2-tu2 teh hian2-chhut pun2-leng2. Bo5 phah-sng3 chui2 e5 lat8 siuN-kiong5, lang5 tong3-boe7-tiau5, tong7 ke3-lai5, tong7 ke3-khi3, chit8 te3 chioh8 tong7 ke3 chit8 te3 chioh8, chhin-chhiuN7 chha5-phe3 phu5-lai5 phu5-khi3 bo5 tiaN7 bo5 tioh8. Cheng3 lang5 khoaN3-kiN3 chit-e5 cheng5-keng2, long2-chong2 gang7-gang7, bo5 hoat-tou7 thang kiu3--i. Ui2-poe3 si2 ti7 toa7 lau5-chui2 e5 tiong-kan. 
  Li7-khui Ui2-poe3 tim5-loh8 chui2 si2 e5 sou2-chai7 bo5 loa7 hng7, ho5--nih8 u7 chit8 e5 chioh8-chhui3, pun2-toe7 lang5 kio3-choe3 ¡§Bo5-kiu3 Chhui3,¡¨ i3-su3 si7 kong2, chhui3 e5 teng2-si3 lau5-chui2 khah ban7, lang5 poah8-loh8 iau2-ku2 u7 tit-tioh8 kiu3 e5 ki-hoe7. Ke3 chit-e5 chhui3, chui2-se3 thai3 kin2, lang5 tim5--loh8, hoaN7-teng2 sui u7 kang2 chheng-ban7 lang5, iah8 si7 gang7-gang7 khoaN3 i si2 na7-tiaN7. Chit-e5 chioh8-chhui3 khiok bo5 loa7 toa7, peng5-siong5 lang5 long2 bo5 soe3-ji7. Chit-e5 chhui3 sit8-chai7 si7 siN-si2 e5 kai3-han7, ti7 chhui3 e5 teng2-si3 iau2-ku2 u7 siN3-mia7 e5 ng3-bang7, kau3 e7-si3 tek-khak tim5 si2. 
  Cha2-jit8 Khong2-chu2 bat kong2, ¡§Lang5 e5 siN3-mia7 chhin-chhiuN7 ho5-chui2 tit8-tit8 lau5--loh8-khi3, jit8-mi5 bo5 soah.¡¨ Tioh8 chai lan2 siN3-mia7 iah8 u7 bo5-kiu3 chhui3, iau2-be7 kau3 chhui3, iau2-ku2 u7 hoan2-hoe2 koe2-piN3 tit-tioh8 kiu3 e5 ki-hoe7, chit8 e7 ke3 chhui3, chiu7 bo5 tit-tioh8 kiu3 e5 ng3-bang7. Chit-e5 chhui3, lang5 long2 bo5 koan-sim, in-ui7 lang5 peng5-an ke3 jit8, ti7 bo5 phah bo5 sng3 e5 si5 chiu7 ke3--khi3. Sou2-i2 lan2 eng-kai si5-si5 khek-khek soe3-ji7 tiuN-ti5. 
  ChhiaN2 mng7 khoaN3 chheh e5 peng5-iu2, siat-su2 li2 u7 chhin-chhek peng5-iu2 ke3-si3, li2 teh sang3 chong3 e5 si5, kiam2 bo5 siuN7, lang5 e5 siN-si2 bo5 tiaN7-tioh8, liong5-sim khoaN3-kiN3 hit-e5 cheng5-keng2, kiam2 bo5 siu7 kam2-chhiok? Kiam2-chhai2 li2 ngou2-jian5 tu2-tioh8 gui5-hiam2, hiam2-hiam2 si2, ti7 kiaN-hiaN5 e5 si5, liong5-sim tek-khak hoat-hian7. Koh, kiam2-chhai2 li2 tu2-tioh8 phoa3-piN7, ki3-tit pat8 lang5 tu2-tioh8 chit ho7 piN7 si2--e5 chin choe7, chai7 li2 siuN7, taN li2 tu2--tioh8, tek-khak bo5 ng3-bang7 u7 siN3-mia7. Kai-chai3 ti7 bo5 phah-sng3 e5 si5, li2 sou2 chiah8 e5 ioh8 u7 eng3-hau7, piN7-se3 chiam7-chiam7 ho2, li2 e5 siN3-mia7 chhin-chhiuN7 koh khioh--tioh8, chit si5 li2 e5 thian-liong5, iah8 tek-khak hoat-hian7. Li2 ki3-jian5 tit-tioh8 thiN e5 un-tian2, kiam2 m7 si7 Siong7-te3 keng2-seng2--li2--mah? Li2 iu5-goan5 be7 bat sin3-hok8 Kiu3 Chu2, m7 kheng2 khiam-hu sim seng5-siu7 ka3-si7, kiam2 bo5 siuN7 teng2-bin7 sou2 kong2 tak8 hang7, iah8 thang choe3 li2 e5 bo5-kiu3 chhui3--mah? Siong7-te3 kong2, ¡§Goa2 e5 Sin5, tek-khak bo5 eng2-oan2 kap lang5 saN-chiN.¡¨ Koh kong2, ¡§Li2 m7-thang phah-biat8 Seng3 Sin5 e5 kam2-tong7.¡¨ 
